Company Profile
Sector: Industrials
Industry: Electrical Equipment
Sub-Industry: Electrical Components
Hillcrest Laboratories, Inc. designs, develops, and produces electronic components. The Company offers sensor modules, pointer remote, wireless presenter, and multi-platform motion software. Hillcrest Laboratories markets its products worldwide.




