Hillcrest Laboratories, Inc. is a supplier of software and hardware for motion-enabled products and widely recognized for pioneering Smart TVs. Based in Rockville, Maryland, the company is funded by NEA, AllianceBernstein, Columbia Capital, and Grotech Ventures.






